The EFF has sent its condolences to the Malema family. JOHANNESBURG - The EFF has confirmed their leader Julius Malema will be speaking at their final rally despite suffering a personal loss this weekend. The party sent its condolences to the Malema family. READ: Malema's grandmother dies Malema's grandmother Sarah Malema died on Saturday morning. The EFF stated Malema would still address the Tshela Thupa rally on Sunday at the Orlando Stadium in Soweto.